{"title":"Rivendell’s Bicycle Fan Club","link":"https://theradavist.com/rivendells-bicycle-fan-club/","date":1705504334000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"666\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/bfc-patch-2-1.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/bfc-patch-2-1.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/bfc-patch-2-1.jpg?resize=768,511&amp;quality=75 768w\" /></p>\n<p>Rivendell are fans of the good ol’ fashioned pedal bike and have made a series of goods showcasing their love. The Bicycle Fan Club patches, stickers membership cards, and caps are all in stock now and shipping from <a href=\"https://www.rivbike.com/collections/bicycle-fan-club?mc_cid=58d4e2075a&amp;mc_eid=081ebe17bd\" target=\"_blank\">Rivendell</a>.<span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/bfc-membershipcard-1.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/bfc-membershipcard-1.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/bfc-membershipcard-1.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/bfc-membershipcard-1.jpg?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/BFC-Stubby-Hat-1.jpg\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/BFC-Stubby-Hat-1.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/BFC-Stubby-Hat-1.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/BFC-Stubby-Hat-1.jpg?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w\" /></p>\n<p><em>The best part is, BFC-branded hats, shirts, buttons, pins, patches, stickers, and so on go to a good cause. All of the 2024 U.S.A. sales profits (retail price minus invoice price) go to <a href=\"https://826valencia.org/\" target=\"_blank\">826 Valencia</a>, a non-profit started by author Dave Eggers to help underserved children develop their reading and writing skills. Rivendell absorbs associated admin &amp; mailing costs.</em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/rivendells-bicycle-fan-club/\">Rivendell’s Bicycle Fan Club</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"21885da8b1756e1f2b307938a53d449b53abb4882cb4813ea3d917f768ff03ce","category":"Cycling"}